HEADWORD: Wash-off
<hw>Wash"-off`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Calico
Printing)</fld> <def>Capable of being washed off; not permanent or
durable; -- said of colors not fixed by steaming or otherwise.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

